name: Alice/Breaker
description: Alice felt an overpowering boredom as she sat next to the river. Seemingly out of nowhere, she spotted a white rabbit scurry off in a hurry. She was compelled to follow the creature.

name: Snow White/Breaker
description: The mirror drove the girl mad. So many people were captivated by her beauty. She went to meet the prince, and yet...

name: Red Riding Hood/Crusher
description: It was intended to be an easy task. It was just a simple meal, after all. But the tale never unfolds that way. When an incorrectly buttoned shirt was noticed too late...

name: Cinderella/Gunner
description:
While she largely accepted it,
her life was nothing but misery...
Until a fairy took pity on
the meak girl and cast a spell on her.
That was when the no longer helpless girl
realized what strength and power truly were...

name: Pinocchio/Crusher
description: The puppet Geppetto made was a mere misfit. Pinocchio desperately struggled through life with the hope of becoming a real boy. But would his wish ever come true?

name: Sleeping Beauty/Crusher
description:
"Blessing" and "curse."
Her life was ruled
by conflicting wishes.
What tale awaits the girl who
wakes from a 100-year slumber?

name: Gretel/Breaker
description:
The siblings got lost
in the forest. The old woman in a gingerbread
house patiently awaited their arrival.
Their love got them through that ordeal.
But the real terror
awaited elsewhere...

name: Princess Kaguya/Paladin
description:
The bamboo cutter's
heart raced in his chest.
He couldn't shake the feeling that
there was something else in the forest.
His fears were realized when he cut open a
shining stalk of bamboo and found a girl inside.

she wouldn't win her true love over...
